1.  package com.msb.filter;
2.  import javax.servlet.*;
3.  import javax.servlet.annotation.WebFilter;
4.  import javax.servlet.annotation.WebInitParam;
5.  import java.io.IOException;
6.  /**
7.   * @Author: Ma HaiYang
8.   * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001
9.   */
10. @WebFilter(urlPatterns = "/myServlet1.do")
11. public class Filter0_MyFilter implements Filter {
12.     @Override
13.     public void init(FilterConfig filterConfig) throws ServletException {
14.     }
15.     @Override
16.     public void doFilter(ServletRequest servletRequest, ServletResponse
    servletResponse, FilterChain filterChain) throws IOException,
    ServletException {
17.         System.out.println("MyFilter0   在过滤请求 ");
18.         filterChain.doFilter(servletRequest,servletResponse);
19.         System.out.println("MyFilter0   在过滤响应");
20.     }
21.     @Override
22.     public void destroy() {
23.     }
24. }

 




1.  package com.msb.filter;
2.  import javax.servlet.*;
3.  import javax.servlet.annotation.WebFilter;
4.  import javax.servlet.annotation.WebInitParam;
5.  import java.io.IOException;
6.  import java.util.Enumeration;
7.  /**
8.   * @Author: Ma HaiYang
9.   * @Description: MircoMessage:Mark_7001
10.  */
11. @WebFilter(urlPatterns = "/myServlet1.do",initParams =
    {@WebInitParam(name="realname",value
    ="zhangsan"),@WebInitParam(name="charset",value ="utf-8")})
12. public class Filter1_MyFilter implements Filter {
13.     @Override
14.     public void init(FilterConfig filterConfig) throws ServletException {
15.         // 获取初始化的一些参数
16.         String realname = filterConfig.getInitParameter("realname");
17.         System.out.println("realname:"+realname);
18.         Enumeration<String> pNames = filterConfig.getInitParameterNames();
19.         while(pNames.hasMoreElements()){
20.             String pName = pNames.nextElement();
21.            
    System.out.println(pName+":"+filterConfig.getInitParameter(pName));
22.         }
23.     }
24.     @Override
25.     public void doFilter(ServletRequest servletRequest, ServletResponse
    servletResponse, FilterChain filterChain) throws IOException,
    ServletException {
26.         System.out.println("MyFilter1   在过滤请求 ");
27.         filterChain.doFilter(servletRequest,servletResponse);
28.         System.out.println("MyFilter1   在过滤响应");
29.     }
30.     @Override
31.     public void destroy() {
32.     }
33. }
